track_notes: Starts at power line access road and circumnavigates  property line by bushwhacking to reach hiking trail. Trail joins remnant of Old Mine Rd. that becomes single track through manzanita. Last 0.5 mile to summit is grueling bushwhack/pathfinding through dense manzanita. This hike is harder than you think...
track_title: Summit via trails and manzanita bushwhack
